In that case, you can make the email a bit more casual and friendly, since you know the person. Here's a revised sample:

Subject: Help Needed - Job Opportunities at Citi Chennai

Hi [Name],

Hope you're doing well! I'm reaching out because I'm currently looking for new opportunities and I thought of you. I know you work at Citi Chennai, and I was wondering if you could keep an eye out for any suitable openings that might be a good fit for me.

If you come across anything, could you please let me know? I'd really appreciate your help and recommendation. I've attached my updated resume for your reference.

Thanks in advance for your time and assistance. Look forward to hearing from you soon.

Best regards,

[Your Name]

This version is a bit more relaxed and friendly, while still being professional. It also shows that you value their opinion and would appreciate their help.
